It\'s in much earlier canon, too.  The Terrans invented
the jump drive more or less by accident while mining
the asteroid belt.  I think that the Solomani Alien
Module discusses it, as well as other GDW and DGP
materials.

Of course, the true story is that a Vilani ship
crashed near Roswell, New Mexico in 1947, and the
United States government spent a long time figuring
out how it worked.  After the United States took over
the United Nations through domination of the World
Trade Organization, it started a series of top-secret
probes into nearby space to find the Vilani and learn
their weaknesses.  Once it was sure that the Vilani
