These numbers are pretty bad, as expected.  Can you image fueling up your
J-6 Yacht and having 112 possible jump destinations to choose from?  Yikes!

I\'ve already used a lot of bandwidth for a single post, so I\'ll stop here.
Remember - these numbers are for Jump-6.  If we limit the jump capability,
the results get much more interesting (and encouraging, ...and shorter,
too).  So, anyone interested in seeing this same table at max Jump-3?

Kurtis
