a good change of having gas giants as fuel sources; very important in a
Traveller universe.

I did some work on the Gleise a while ago.  I believe in that data a jump 3
would get you pretty much anyware with patience, while a jump 1 was worthless.
The analysis I did was based around generating "clusters" of mutually accessable
stars for a given jump number, then determining how many seperate clusters the
database boiled down to.

