I know I haven\'t looked at 8+ Digests and I\'m sure that someone else would
have been mentioned this, but as an Aussie growing up with our then one and
only Government TV channel, who can forget the visual splendor of that
infamous generic sci-fi location, the BBC quarry. Man I must have seen that
in twenty odd shows, Dr Who (every second episode it seemed) and Blake\'s
Seven being the prime contenders.

