> defining both current and future communications technologies,
> including those that may be purely science fiction which might work
> well within the Traveller setting.  The Communications skill within
> Traveller is, at least for me, too broad, too encompassing.  If one
> were to break down the communications technology discipline into
> separate technical areas of expertise or subspecialities what would
