uninhabitable.  Otherwise the inhabitants would just live at the north and
south poles.  What\'s a good distance for this from an F9 VI?  Can I assume
that the planet\'s mean temp will be found at the twilight band in general?
Something tells me there\'s going to be a sinusoidal relationship that I\'m
missing...

Any thoughts on these or other aspects of my idea are welcomed.

Thanks,
Charles C.
