The fact that there *has* to be atmospheric circulation (ie *weather*,
and some "climate") or else all the atmosphere will wind up in a big
stack at the middle of darkside, melting away on one side and building
up on the other as the planet slowly rotates.

Actually, any such figures are going to be a *guess* since we don\'t
*have* a planet with anything *close* to those specs to work with. 

