> south poles.

The north and south poles won\'t be much different in temp from anyplace
else along the teminator. But if you make the terminator unihabitable
what are they going to use for food? You can\'t grow anything on the
dark side. 

I suppose it\'d work if you made only the "hot pole" habitable. 

