the right to add a prefix or suffix to one\'s name. It is a very direct
invitation to be part of learned debate in the Imperium.

I\'m even considering the use of a noble language, sort of like Latin in the
medieval period, but more like the French language during the Enlightenment.
Your own mileage may vary, of course, since I\'m diverging from standard
canon for my own Traveller universe.

