- ----
Subject: Re: Question: Origin of term \'Munchkin\'
Date: Sat, 21 Jun 1997 00:03:42 GMT
From: ncc1701i@hotmail.com (Mark Campbell)
Organization:None
Newsgroups: rec.games.frp.misc, rec.games.design
