>>Almost everybody now plays one of the following, at least part time: D&D,
>>Palladium Games, GURPS, Hero, WW-Storyteller. Idicators of a market
>>correction.
>
>I would remove Hero from that list.  Champions was very popular in the
>past, but it doesn\'t remotely get the sales that L5R or Deadlands has now.
